Introduction

Sio is a South Korean singer under Massive E&C. She used to be a part of the girl group FIFTY FIFTY. The group officially made their debut with “The Fifty” released on November 18, 2022. She left the group with members Aran and Saena after the group's first comeback

In a legal turn of events, FIFTY FIFTY initiated a lawsuit against Attrakt Creative Group on June 28, 2023, citing contract violations and damage to their reputation. Further developments on October 23 revealed that Attrakt had ended its exclusive contracts with group members Saena, Sio, and Aran as of October 19, 2023.
